# RoboLedger V5.2.23: Fidelity & Logic Wiring Update

This update hardens the V5 shell, ensuring data integrity across account switches and providing enhanced search-as-you-type capabilities.

## 🔍 Smart Search & Action Bar
The Action Bar now supports live forensic searching.
- [x] **Live Search Engine**: Toggle search via the magnifying glass to filter descriptions, Ref#, or Account# in real-time.
- [x] **ESC to Dismiss**: High-fidelity UX—press Escape to clear search and return to the primary view.

## 🔄 Bidirectional Ref# & Pill Sync
Changing the account name now reflects everywhere instantly.
- [x] **Custom Pill Labels**: Changing the Ref# (e.g., to `CHQ3`) now instantly updates the Account Switcher pill label.
- [x] **Consolidated Wiring**: Removed duplicate logic to ensure a single, stable source of truth for account naming.

## 🏛️ Account & Metadata Fidelity
Fixed property naming mismatches to ensure absolute forensic accuracy.
- [x] **Canonical Metadata**: Unified property names to fix the "NO METADATA" bug. Inst, Transit, and Account# now show up correctly in the Action Bar.
- [x] **Account Pruning**: Removed redundant default accounts to ensure the UI only shows relevant data pills.

## ⚡ Session Recovery Refinement
- [x] **Subtle Notice Styling**: The recovery banner is now styled as a professional, non-aggressive amber notice (`v5-notice-banner`).
- [x] **Deep Purge**: Choosing "Start New" now performs a full-ledger reset and clears the UI state.

---
*RoboLedger V5: Forensic Integrity. Infinite Scale.*
- **COA Tagging**: Integrated the "All roads lead to COA" philosophy—transactions map to categories via high-fidelity tags rather than sub-ledgers.

## 🛠️ Parser Polarity Fix
Resolved a critical bug where all transactions were bucketed as "Credits". 
- **Debit Detection**: The engine now correctly identifies outgoings based on amount signs (`-`) and description keywords (`PURCHASE`, `WITHDRAWAL`).

---
**RoboLedger V5 is now functionally audited and performance-hardened.** 🚀
